No. 108,

Orig.

Nebraska v. Wyoming et al.

Motions of the parties respecting oral argument granted in part and denied in part, and the time and order allotted are: 20 minutes to Wyoming, 10 minutes to Colorado, 15 minutes to Nebraska, and 15 minutes to the United States. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., ante, p. 996.]
